text:
(Before It's News)
By Lisa Haven
By now you have all witnessed the 2017 Super Bowl event where the New England Patriots defeated the Atlanta Falcons. Additionally, you likely witnessed the Illuminati’s yearly “Satan” dedication halftime show, which this year featured Satan’s own, Lady Gaga, who played the role of the female succubus rather well. But one thing you may not have heard is that one player on the Patriots team is refusing to go to the White House. One of the benefits to winning the Super Bowl is that you get to visit the president. However one team member has refused, and this same team member held up a “black power” sign during the 2017 widely broadcast event. I believe when you find out, you’ll be stunned.
